data.description: **OPEN HOUSE THIS SATURDAY 0/13 9-4** **Assumable FHA loan below 4% if you qualify**Welcome to this stunning contemporary home nestled in the heart of San Antonio, Texas, offering a perfect blend of modern luxury and practical functionality. Boasting a thoughtfully designed open floor plan, this 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence is a testament to both style and comfort. As you step inside, you are greeted by a seamlessly integrated living space that effortlessly connects the living room, kitchen, and dining area, creating an inviting atmosphere for both daily living and entertaining. The main level features the primary bedroom, providing a serene retreat. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms, complemented by a convenient Jack and Jill bathroom, complete the downstairs living quarters. For those who appreciate the finer things, a formal dining room offers an elegant space for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories. Ascend the stairs to discover a media room that provides a versatile space for relaxation or entertainment. An additional bedroom and bathroom upstairs add flexibility to accommodate guests or create a private home office. The covered back patio, surrounded by mature trees, invites you to relax outdoors. This home is situated near shopping centers and schools, ensuring convenience for daily activities. Whether you're connected to Lackland Air Force Base, UTSA, or other major employers, the central location enhances your daily life. Immerse yourself in the vibrant San Antonio lifestyle while enjoying the comfort and sophistication of this contemporary residence. Don't miss the opportunity to schedule a private tour and envision life in this modern haven in the heart of Texas.
